text: Kim Ik-jong (born 10 May 1941) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
